f Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010026, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Reform conditions of Your servant and caliph with those means by which You have reformed conditions of Your messengers and prophets. Surround him with the angels and support him with the Holy Spirit. Appoint protectors from the front and behind him, (those) who would guard him from all troubles and calamities. Convert his fear into security, (so that) he may worship only You and doesn’t associate anybody with You. Do not make any of Your creatures an authority over Your vicegerent. Permit him to fight against Your enemies and his enemies and include me among his helpers. Surely You possess power over everything.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Parwardigaar! Jin wasaael se Tu ne apne ambiya o mursaleen ke haalaat ki islaah farmaayi hai, apne abd’e khaas aur ja-nasheen ke haalaat ki bhi islaah farma. Malaayeka uske gird rahe aur Roohul Qudoos uski taaeed kare. Uske saamne aur pase-pusht (peechhe) aise muhaafiz rahe jo usey har museebat aur aafat se bachaate rahe, uska khouf un se tabdeel ho jaaye. Woh Teri ibaadat mein masroof rahe aur shirk ka koi nishaan na rahe, kisi shakhs ko Tere Wali par iqtedaar haasil na ho aur usey apne aur uske dushman se jehaad ki ijaazat de de aur hamein uske ansaar o awaan mein jagah de, Tu kaayenaat ki har shai par qaadir hai.", "Urdu": "پروردگارا! جن وسائیل سے تو نے اپنے انبیا و مرسلین کے حالات کی اصلاح فرمائی ہے، اپنے عبدِ خاص اور جانشین کے حالات کی بھی اصلاح فرما، ملائکہ اس کے گرد رہے روح القدوس اس کی تائید کرے، اس کے سامنے اور پسِ پشت ایسے محافظ رہے جو اسے ہر مصیبت اور آفت سے بچاتے رہے، اس کا خوف ان سے تبدیل ہو جائے، وہ تیری عبادت میں مصروف رہے اور شرک کا کوئی شائبہ نہ رہے، کسی شخص کو تیرے ولی پر اقتدار حاصل نہ ہو اور اسے اپنے اور اس کے دشمن سے جہاد کی اجازت دے دے اور ہمیں اس کے انصار و عوان میں جگہ دے، تو کائنات کی ہر شے پر قادر ہے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA ASLEH A’BDE-KA WA KHLEE-FATA-KA BEMAA ASLAH-TA BEHI AMBE-YAA-A-KA WA ROSO-LAKA WA HUFFA-HU BE-MALAA-E-KATE-KA WA AYYID-HU BE-ROOHIL QUDDU-SE MIN I’NDE-KA WASLUK-HU MIM BAIYNE YADAIY-HE WA MIN KHLAFE-HI RASA-DAN YAH-FAZOO NAHU MIN KULLE SOO-IN WA ABDIL-HO MIN BA’DE KHAUFE-HI AMNAN YA’BODO-KA LAA YUSRE-KO BEKA SHAI-AN WALAA TAJ-A’L LE-AHA-DIM MIN KHALQE-KA A’LAA WALIYYE-KA SULTANAN WA-ZAN LAHU FEE JEHAA-DE A’DOO-WEKA WAJ-A’LNEE MIN ANSAARE-HI INNA-KA A’LAA KULLE SHAI-IN QADEE-RUN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ اَصْلِحْ عَبْدَکَ وَخَلِیفَتَکَ بِمَا اَصْلَحْتَ بِہٖ اَنْبِۢیَآئَکَ وَرُسُلَکَ وَحُفَّہٗ بِمَلَائِکَتِکَ وَاَیِّدْہٗ بِرُوْحِ الْقُدُسِ مِنْ عِنْدِکَ وَاسْلُکْہٗ مِنْۢ بَیْنِ یَدَیْہِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِہٖ رَصَدًا یَحْفَظُوْنَہٗ مِنْ کُلِّ سُوْئٍ وَّاَبْدِلْہُ مِنْ بَعْدِ خَوْفِہٖ اَمْنًا یَعْبُدُکَ لَایُشْرِکُ بِکَ شَیْئًا وَلَاتَجْعَلْ لِاَحَدٍ مِّنْ خَلْقِکَ عَلٰی وَلِیِّکَ سُلْطَانًا وَاْذَنْ لَّہٗ فِیْ جِھَادِ عَدُوِّکَ وَاجْعَلْنِیْ مِنْ اَنْصَارِہٖ اِنَّکَ عَلٰی کُلِّ شَیْٓءٍ قَدِیْرٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": 